  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I was sorting through my old game discs. Among them, there were many games I played when I was a kid. All of them were labeled...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All of them except <strong>one.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It immediately caught my attention, and I decided to try playing it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>What bad could it possibly do?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There were game files on it. Nothing unusual, except for the strange name.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I launched it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>What is this? A children’s game?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>It's so cute and colorful, but why do I have a feeling like something’s <strong>wrong..?</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3578040/extras/27a8eca89b0ef64a4bddced78879cb94.avif?t=1765368811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3578040/extras_big/27a8eca89b0ef64a4bddced78879cb94.avif?t=1765368811 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>This ominous eclipse…</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3578040/extras/1efb3b51422ec5a10b4f1052259f5705.avif?t=1765368811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3578040/extras_big/1efb3b51422ec5a10b4f1052259f5705.avif?t=1765368811 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>...Hey!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>My name is Sunshine!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Yes, yes, it's me! Will you help me?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>What are you waiting for?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>I'm waiting for you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3578040/extras/63246cff92bf94878c2ff440608ec9e8.avif?t=1765368811\" width=400 height=351 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In our game you will find:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— Various mini-games and puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— Point-and-click quest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— A large number of CG-arts and animations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— The presence of choices that affect the ending and events in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— Various secrets and Easter eggs.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I was sorting through my old game discs. Among them, there were many games I played when I was a kid. All of them were labeled...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All of them except <strong>one.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It immediately caught my attention, and I decided to try playing it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>What bad could it possibly do?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There were game files on it. Nothing unusual, except for the strange name.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I launched it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>What is this? A children’s game?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>It's so cute and colorful, but why do I have a feeling like something’s <strong>wrong..?</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3578040/extras/27a8eca89b0ef64a4bddced78879cb94.avif?t=1765368811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3578040/extras_big/27a8eca89b0ef64a4bddced78879cb94.avif?t=1765368811 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>This ominous eclipse…</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3578040/extras/1efb3b51422ec5a10b4f1052259f5705.avif?t=1765368811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3578040/extras_big/1efb3b51422ec5a10b4f1052259f5705.avif?t=1765368811 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>...Hey!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>My name is Sunshine!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Yes, yes, it's me! Will you help me?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>What are you waiting for?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>I'm waiting for you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3578040/extras/63246cff92bf94878c2ff440608ec9e8.avif?t=1765368811\" width=400 height=351 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In our game you will find:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— Various mini-games and puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— Point-and-click quest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— A large number of CG-arts and animations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— The presence of choices that affect the ending and events in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— Various secrets and Easter eggs.</p>",
